         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne botan. Gardens ¶ 28/6/66 ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ It having come to the knowledge of the Trustees of the Royal Park that the building used lately as a temporary lunatic Asylum has become vacant I have the...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">66.06.28</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To James McCulloch</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">A345 Royal Park Zoological Society letter and minute book, pp. 24-5, Mitchell Library, State Library of New South Wales, Sydney.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne botan. Gardens</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">28/6/66</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>It having come to the knowledge of the Trustees of the Royal Park that the building used lately as a temporary lunatic Asylum has become vacant I have the honor by direction of the trustees to point out for your consideration that possession may be given of this building to the Trustees.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The unfitness of the building alluded to for the safe custody of Lunatics is generally<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">W</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">or</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">d(s)</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>omitted?</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>only lately three of them escaped, one entered a house in the vicinity occupied by women &amp; children and some time elapsed before he was pursued by a keeper, and thus the safety of the family became actually jeopardized Many houses have been erected near the building, where the families of working men are left without protection during the day hours, thus it is highly probable, that some serious accident will happen if insane if insane<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">words repeated</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                     </p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; font-weight: bold; color: #C00000; "
                        xml:lang="en">Going from one page to another?</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>people should continue to be allowed on the spot.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The Trustees direct me to draw your attention to the circumstances under which the building was allotted<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="background-color: #FFFF00; ">to to</seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>its temporary purpose and they express now a hope, that you will be pleased to allow it to revert to them and that the key may be given to the Ranger of the Park.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See G. Sprigg to M, 22 June 1866<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #0070C0; ">(in this edition as 66-06-22c)</seg>: 'At the time the lunatics were first placed there namely two years ago the Trustees of the Park were informed that the accommodation was only required for a short time'<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #0070C0; ">.</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #0070C0; ">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>For the original concurrence to the use of the powder magazine as an asylum see M to J. McCulloch, 21 October 1863 (in this edition as 64-10-21a) and notes thereto</seg>.</p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; font-weight: bold; color: #C00000; "
                        xml:lang="en">Any annotations or minutes?</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your most obed. servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>signed F. Mueller</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Hon. Sec. to the Trustees of the Roy. Park</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">The honorable the Chief Secretary</p>
         </div>
